# Pliex Engineering Rules

## Code
- Clean Code (Uncle Bob) principles
- Small, single-purpose functions and components
- Intention-revealing names everywhere
- Separate: UI / validation / business logic / API / service / data / errors
- No duplication — extract shared logic
- Simple over clever

## Stack
Next.js · TypeScript · App Router · Tailwind · shadcn/ui · Supabase · OpenAI · Resend · 

## Structure
- /src/app         → pages and routes
- /src/components  → reusable UI
- /src/lib         → services, AI, DB, utils
- /src/types       → shared TypeScript types

## Docs
Update the relevant .md doc on every feature or schema change.
Docs live in /docs — never let them drift from code.

## Constraints
- Google auth only
- Single owner, single business per MVP
- No billing, no teams, no enterprise